flows.name: exposure
flows.rate_expression: default_infectivity*susceptibles*(base_contact_home*isolated_asymptomatics*isolation_effect_on_asym_contacts*policy_multiplier_home*(1 - infectivity_reduction_for_asym)*piecewise((1, True), (1, True))/total_population + base_contact_home*isolated_symtomatics_mild*isolation_effect_on_sym_contacts*policy_multiplier_home*piecewise((1, True), (1, True))/total_population + base_contact_home*policy_multiplier_home*quarantine_effect_on_asym_contacts*quarantined_asymptomatics*(1 - infectivity_reduction_for_asym)*piecewise((1, True), (1, True))/total_population + base_contact_home*policy_multiplier_home*quarantine_effect_on_sym_contacts*quarantined_symtomatics_mild*piecewise((1, True), (1, True))/total_population + infectious_asymptomatics*(1 - infectivity_reduction_for_asym)*piecewise((lockdown_effect_on_contacts*(base_contact_home + base_contact_school + base_contact_work + base_contacts_other)*piecewise((1, True), (1, True)), False), (base_contact_home*policy_multiplier_home*piecewise((1, True), (1, True)) + base_contact_school*policy_multiplier_school*piecewise((1, True), (1, True)) + base_contact_work*policy_multiplier_work*piecewise((1, True), (1, True)) + base_contacts_other*policy_multiplier_other*piecewise((1, True), (1, True)), True))/total_population + infectious_symptomatics_mild*piecewise((lockdown_effect_on_contacts*(base_contact_home + base_contact_school + base_contact_work + base_contacts_other)*piecewise((1, True), (1, True)), False), (base_contact_home*policy_multiplier_home*piecewise((1, True), (1, True)) + base_contact_school*policy_multiplier_school*piecewise((1, True), (1, True)) + base_contact_work*policy_multiplier_work*piecewise((1, True), (1, True)) + base_contacts_other*policy_multiplier_other*piecewise((1, True), (1, True)), True))/total_population)*piecewise((loastartlevel + ramp((loaendlevel - loastartlevel)/(loaendtime - loastarttime), loastarttime, loaendtime), time < april_14), (loastartlevel + ramp((loaendlevel - loastartlevel)/(loaendtime - loastarttime), loastarttime, loaendtime), True))

flows.name: hospital_admissions
flows.rate_expression: Min(incoming_demand_on_hospital/time_step, Max(0, (healthcare_capacity_multiplier*normal_hospital_beds_per_person*patients_per_unit*total_population*(-(1 - ppe_availability)*(infectious_asymptomatics + recovered_asymtomatics + recovered_from_hospital + recovered_isolated_symptomatic_mild + recovered_mild + susceptibles)/total_population + (infectious_asymptomatics + recovered_asymtomatics + recovered_from_hospital + recovered_isolated_symptomatic_mild + recovered_mild + susceptibles)/total_population) - infected_sym_serious_hospital)*xidz(incoming_demand_on_hospital, incoming_demand_on_hospital, 1)/time_step))

flows.name: hospital_overflow
flows.rate_expression: Max(0, incoming_demand_on_hospital/time_step - Max(0, (healthcare_capacity_multiplier*normal_hospital_beds_per_person*patients_per_unit*total_population*(-(1 - ppe_availability)*(infectious_asymptomatics + recovered_asymtomatics + recovered_from_hospital + recovered_isolated_symptomatic_mild + recovered_mild + susceptibles)/total_population + (infectious_asymptomatics + recovered_asymtomatics + recovered_from_hospital + recovered_isolated_symptomatic_mild + recovered_mild + susceptibles)/total_population) - infected_sym_serious_hospital)*xidz(incoming_demand_on_hospital, incoming_demand_on_hospital, 1)/time_step))

flows.name: icu_admissions
flows.rate_expression: Min(fr_requiring_icu*delay3i(hospital_admissions, delay_worsening, 0), Max(0, (healthcare_capacity_multiplier*normal_icu_capacity_per_person*patients_per_unit*total_population*(-(1 - ppe_availability)*(infectious_asymptomatics + recovered_asymtomatics + recovered_from_hospital + recovered_isolated_symptomatic_mild + recovered_mild + susceptibles)/total_population + (infectious_asymptomatics + recovered_asymtomatics + recovered_from_hospital + recovered_isolated_symptomatic_mild + recovered_mild + susceptibles)/total_population) - infected_sym_extreme_icu)*xidz(fr_requiring_icu*delay3i(hospital_admissions, delay_worsening, 0), fr_requiring_icu*delay3i(hospital_admissions, delay_worsening, 0), 1)/time_step))

flows.name: icu_overflow
flows.rate_expression: Max(0, fr_requiring_icu*delay3i(hospital_admissions, delay_worsening, 0) - Max(0, (healthcare_capacity_multiplier*normal_icu_capacity_per_person*patients_per_unit*total_population*(-(1 - ppe_availability)*(infectious_asymptomatics + recovered_asymtomatics + recovered_from_hospital + recovered_isolated_symptomatic_mild + recovered_mild + susceptibles)/total_population + (infectious_asymptomatics + recovered_asymtomatics + recovered_from_hospital + recovered_isolated_symptomatic_mild + recovered_mild + susceptibles)/total_population) - infected_sym_extreme_icu)*xidz(fr_requiring_icu*delay3i(hospital_admissions, delay_worsening, 0), fr_requiring_icu*delay3i(hospital_admissions, delay_worsening, 0), 1)/time_step))

flows.name: new_cases_reported
flows.rate_expression: fr_symptomatic_tested_isolated*delay3i(symptom_setting, delay_iso_sym, 0) + fraction_iso_asym*delay3i(infection_rate_sum, delay_iso_asym, 0) + (-fr_iso + q_sym + 1)*delay3i(symptom_setting, delay_disease_diagnosis, 0)*Min(0.9, fr_becoming_serious) + delay3i(into_q_sym, net_delay_dprogress_q_sym, 0)*Min(0.9, fr_becoming_serious)
